"A richly defined, innovative experience, Lost Echo is exactly what an iOS adventure should be, capturing the spirit of traditional adventure gaming with all the potential the platform has to offer." -AdventureGamers.com<br />
<br />
"I can't help but be completely and utterly impressed." -IndieGames.com<br />
